sentences: Her father died when she was one week old, leaving her mother, a small-scale farmer, as the family's provider.
Lilian attended school through Form One, the first year of secondary school in Kenya.
Prince Jully died in 1997 and subsequently Princess Jully took over the leadership of the band.
Her 19th album "Aneno Lek" was released in March 2007.
Her next album Wangni Wabiro was released in August 2007.
The title song of the album was dedicated to the Orange Democratic Movement ahead of the 2007 General Election.
In 2010 she released another album Joluo Migingo to Dhi, its title refers to the disputed Migingo Island.
The group performed at the Festival Mundial in Tilburg, Netherlands, in 2007.
